Arrangements have been concluded for a befitting funeral rites of Elder Silas Olekanma of Umuahia in Isuikwuato Local Government Area of Abia State, who transited to glory on December 4, 2022 at the age of 80 years. A release by Barrister Ikechukwu Olekanma on behalf of the family, said there would be a service of songs at his residence in Umuakwua in Isuikwuato Local Government Area of Abia State on Friday, April 29, 2022. The release noted that on Saturday, Aprill 30, 2022 by 9 a.m, his remains would depart the Hakuna Matata Mortuary Okigwe, for Unuakwua, Isuikwato of Abia State. Thereafter, there would be a burial service at his compound by Abosso Apostolic Faith Church of Jesus Christ, while interment follows immediately also at his residence.